rComments: Although it's clear that Professor Mystille is new to teaching, I feel that she did alright, although she mostly just read what was on the slides. That being said, attendance is taken three times at random; each is worth 5%, so don't miss it! She doesn't always reply to emails, so if you have questions, ask them after class.

So far I really like this class! She seems like the nicest prof I've ever met. English is probably not her first language but you can still understand. . Her tests are fair and there are no surprises. Not sure if this is because I'm in a science program taking it as an elective but the course load is very light ! Also you get 15% for attendence.

Seems like it's her first time teaching. Has difficulty communicating in English. Not her area either. Using textbook can contradict what she teaches in class. Not very engaging, and difficult to take seriously, and not just as someone who got plugged into fill this teaching spot at the last minute.
